snippet.title: [HINDI] BGIS 2024 | GRAND FINALS | Day 1 | BGMI
snippet.description:
Welcome to the GRAND FINALS of the BGIS 2024

Feel the pulse-pounding intensity as the top 16 teams converge on the battleground for a shot at ultimate glory in BGIS history. This is more than just a tournament round, it's the climax of the BATTLEGROUNDS MOBILE INDIA SERIES 2024, where dreams soar and legends are made. With a massive prize pool of INR 2 Crores, the stakes are at their peak.

16 Lan Finalists: GLOBAL ESPORTS, TEAM AARU, X SPARK, iQOO SOUL, FS ESPORTS, VASISTA ESPORTS, TEAM TAMILAS, R4VEN ESPORTS, CARNIVAL GAMING, MOGO ESPORTS, TEAM LIMRA, VENOM GAMING, 8 BIT, TEAM INSANE ESPORTS, INFERNO SQUAD, RECKONING ESPORTS.


#MAKEWAVES #BATTLEGROUNDSMOBILEINDIA #INDIAKAGAME #RISEABOVE

snippet.description:
Rate Sipahi on IMDB - https://www.imdb.com/title/tt32765621/

This special film showcases the struggle of Sanatan Vijay, a poor boy aspiring to join the police force as a constable. Dedicated to the hardworking youth of the nation who dare to dream, 'Sipahi' aims to uncover their struggle and inspire everyone. Through Sanatan Vijay's story, the film celebrates resilience and determination, making it a poignant tribute to those who strive to overcome their circumstances and achieve their dreams.

snippet.title: कुरकुरी भिन्डी - इसे चाय के साथ खायें या सब्जी की तरह चावल-रोटी-परांठे के साथ | Crispy Bhindi Recipe
snippet.description:
कुरकुरी भिन्डी, जो सब्जी भी है और स्नैक्स भी, और बनने में समय भी बहुत कम लगे. तो फटाफट बना डालिये,  crispy okra fry,  kurkuri bhindi masala fry, 
#bhindi #snacks #sabji #teatime 

Ingredients for Kurkuri Bhindi
भिंडी - Ladyfinger - 250 grams
नमक - Salt - 1/2 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1/4 tsp
धनिया पाउडर - Coriander powder - 1 tsp
लाल मिर्च - Red chilli - 1/2 tsp
गरम मसाला - Garam masala - 1/2 tsp
चाट मसाला - Chat masala - 1 tsp
चावल का आटा - Rice flour - 4 tbsp
बेसन - Gram flour - 2 tbsp
नमक - Salt - 1/4 tsp
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1/2 tsp

Subscribe for more recipes - 
http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=nishamadhulika

http://www.youtube.com/nishamadhulika

Popatlal so happy and relaxed. And to add to the excitement, a potential wedding opportunity is on the horizon! Will Popatlal finally tie the knot and start a new chapter in his life?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Beetroot Rava idli :

Curd- 1 Cup
beetroot juice-  2 Cups (total)
Roasted rava-  2 Cups
Salt( according to taste )
Ghee-  1 tbs
Mustard Seeds - 1tsp
ginger-  1 tbs
green chilli  - 2 nos
Curry Leaves

Eno-  1 tsp (5gm)
.......................................................

Salt( according to taste )
Water

Mustard Seeds - 1 tsp
Dry red - 3 - 4 nos
Curry Leaves
Coriander leaves

Welcome to our Tamil Devotional Channel, your ultimate destination for soulful and uplifting Tamil devotional songs. Dive into the divine with our carefully curated collections designed to inspire and bring peace to your soul every day of the week.

Daily Devotional Songs:

Special Devotional Collections:
* Shiva Tamil Devotional Songs: Celebrate the power and grace of Lord Shiva.

* Muruga Tamil Devotional Songs: Invoke the valor and blessings of Lord Muruga.
* Hanuman Tamil Devotional Songs: Feel the strength and devotion of Lord Hanuman.
* Amman Tamil Devotional Songs: Honor the divine mother in her various forms.

Special Occasions and Deities:
* Amavasai Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs for the new moon day rituals.
* Pradosham Tamil Devotional Songs: Hymns for the auspicious Pradosham period.

* Guru Tamil Devotional Songs: Songs to honor Guru and seek his wisdom.
* Perumal Tamil Devotional Songs: Devote to Lord Perumal with these spiritual songs.

snippet.title: KUCHI ICE | FRUIT POPSICLES | Healthy Homemade Colorful Popsicle Making in Village | Stick Ice Cream
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we make colorful, healthy fruit Popsicles, which are 90s kids' favorite snakes of our childhood. We call these popsicles Kuchi Ice or Stick Ice. We use some healthy fruits, such as Mango, Pomegranate, Grape, and Kiwi, for this ice cream. We use a silicon Popsicle Mold, which is used for making ice Popsicles at home. Finally, we taste this Ice in the summer evening!

Yummy!

snippet.title: Jethalal ने बनाया Match देखने का Plan | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Soda Shop Pe Charcha
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

The men of Gokuldham decide to go to the stadium and watch Tappu's match. Popatlal has different plans. He dreams of watching Sachin's old matches with Sachin at his house. Will Popatlal's dream come true?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 1268-1278
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the more episodes Soda Shop Pe Charcha : 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1kXmkWTsqo2kenKxZ_LfGX

Set in a dystopian future, the movie explores the themes of heroism, mythology, and advanced technology, blending them into a visually stunning narrative. With a significant budget and high expectations, "Kalki 2898 AD" has garnered attention for its ambitious storytelling and star-studded lineup. As fans eagerly awaited its release, the film aimed to set new benchmarks in Indian cinema. But did it live up to the hype?

"Kalki 2898 AD" has sparked a wide range of reactions from audiences and critics alike. Some praised the film for its grand visuals, innovative concepts, and the powerful performances of its star-studded cast, particularly Amitabh Bachchan's commanding presence and Prabhas' compelling portrayal of the titular character. However, others felt that the film's narrative was overly complex and struggled to balance its ambitious ideas, leading to moments of confusion. Despite these mixed reviews, the movie's bold attempt to push the boundaries of Indian cinema is undeniable. Whether it becomes a blockbuster or not, "Kalki 2898 AD" has certainly made a significant impact, igniting discussions about the future of filmmaking in the industry. Its legacy may ultimately be determined by how it influences future projects and the evolution of science fiction in Indian cinema.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

WhatsApp:
http://wa.me/+919946907624
http://wa.me/+919746864111

             देत बानी पानी तबो गांछी बा सुखाईल
             बतिया बा जवन तनी खुल के बाताव
             हामारा से धन काहें मन बा दुखाईल
लड़की= कुँवारे रही जईती ए राजा -2
             आ चढ़ल तिलक फेरवईती कुँआरे रही जईती ए     राजा
             अरे नईहरे में लईका पटईती कुँआरे रही जईती        ए राजा
                      अन्तरा
लड़की= तोहारा ना दाया बाटे अबे देह नाया बाटे
लड़का= धनिया हो बाड़ू तू बहुते मनसोखे
             अँचरे में रखबू की अउरी कुछो होखे
लड़की= ससुरावा ना अईती ए राजा -2
           पापा जी के पईसा बचईती कुँआरे रही जईती        ए राजा
अरे नईहरे में लईका पटईती कुँआरे रही जईती  ए राजा
                     अन्तरा
लड़की= गरम ना सरद बाड़ कईसन तू मरद बाड़ 
लड़का= तूर दिल बोस के ना लीही सभे माजा
            सुनिहे त कहि हे का बोल ना अंकुश राजा
लड़की= दोसर सुख पईती ए राजा -2
             खोल के जवनीया लुटईती कुँआरे रही जईती        ए राजा
अरे नईहरे में लईका पटईती कुँआरे रही जईती ए राजा

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Leta Jaijo Re | Shashwat Sachdev x Sunidhi Chauhan x Chotu Khan
snippet.description:
The legacy of Rajasthani culture echoes its history from its palatial havelis, speaks of furtive & shy romances through its stone walls and sings folk songs of tradition & meticulous courtship, cherished and passed down through generations. 
‘Leta Jaijo Re’ is sung like a love song but experienced as a celebration. The song celebrates the beginning of a young couple’s love story, through the willingness to give away a token of your love. 
Acclaimed music super producer Shashwat Sachdev strings together this piece of cultural story-telling through his global yet rooted pallette weaving beautifully Sunidhi Chauhan’s contemporary prowess. 

*CREDITS*

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.
